OL,3,C'Vengeful' man murdered friend after
OL,4,C'childish' eyebrow prank
OL,6,FA "vengeful" man who murdered a father-
OL,7,Fof-three following a "childish" row
OL,8,Fover a prank he played on him told
OL,9,Fpolice his victim had "fallen on the
OL,10,Fknife" when arrested.
OL,12,FMatthew Higgins, 36, stabbed David
OL,13,FEaton, 37, with a kitchen knife
OL,14,Ffollowing a dispute that included
OL,15,FHiggins shaving off his friend's
OL,16,Feyebrow as he slept, Chester Crown
OL,17,FCourt heard.
