OL,3,C'Vengeful' man murdered friend after
OL,4,C'childish' eyebrow prank
OL,6,FThe day before his murder, a furious
OL,7,FMr Eaton lashed out at Higgins in the
OL,8,Fstreet in Northwich, Cheshire,
OL,9,Fpunching and kicking him, although did
OL,10,Fnot cause any injuries.
OL,12,FThe pair later clashed again at
OL,13,FHiggins's home in Brook Lane as Mr
OL,14,FEaton struck the defendant, but again
OL,15,Fcaused no injuries, the court heard.
OL,17,FJudge Everett said: "It made you
OL,18,Fbehave in a vengeful and vindictive
OL,19,Fway. You decided you were going to do
OL,20,Fsomething about it.
