OL,6,FHiggins then lied to police when he
OL,7,Fclaimed Mr Eaton had "fallen on the
OL,8,Fknife".
OL,10,FThe killer later said he acted in self-
OL,11,Fdefence but a jury rejected his
OL,12,Faccount and convicted him on 9 April
OL,13,Fof murder. He earlier had pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to assaulting a police officer
OL,15,Ffollowing his arrest.
