OL,3,C'Vengeful' man murdered friend after
OL,4,C'childish' eyebrow prank
OL,6,FIn a victim personal statement read to
OL,7,Fthe court, Mr Eaton's mother, Carol,
OL,8,Fsaid her son had a drink problem and
OL,9,F"did not always make the best
OL,10,Fdecisions", but he was a "kind and
OL,11,Fcaring soul who helped others where
OL,12,Fpossible".
OL,14,FShe added: "David was robbed of the
OL,15,Fpossibility of changing his lifestyle."
OL,17,FIn mitigation, Owen Edwards KC said:
OL,18,F"This was a incident between two
OL,19,Ffriends living similar lifestyles. In
OL,20,Fone case a life lost, and in another
OL,21,Fcase a life truly wasted.
