OL,6,F"Alcohol has been the root cause of
OL,7,Fmost problems in his life."
OL,9,FThe 36-year-old was on trial for
OL,10,Faround two and a half weeks at Chester
OL,11,FCrown Court before being found guilty
OL,12,Fby a jury of four men and eight women.
OL,13,FJudge Steven Everett sentenced him to
OL,14,Fa minimum of 18 years.
OL,16,FFollowing sentencing, Detective
OL,17,FInspector Eleanor Atkinson, of
OL,18,FCheshire Constabulary, said: "Higgins
OL,19,Fchose to pick up a knife and let his
OL,20,Fanger get the better of him. That
OL,21,Fdecision had devastating consequences.
