OL,3,C'Vengeful' man murdered friend after
OL,4,C'childish' eyebrow prank
OL,6,F"Despite knowing what he had done, he
OL,7,Fdenied the charge of murder and forced
OL,8,FDavid's loved ones to sit through a
OL,9,Ftwo-and-a-half week trial. But the
OL,10,Fjury saw through his lies and
OL,11,Fconvicted him of murder.
OL,13,F"I welcome the sentence handed down to
OL,14,FHiggins, and while nothing can bring
OL,15,FDavid back to his family and friends,
OL,16,FI hope the fact Higgins is now behind
OL,17,Fbars for his murder will bring them
OL,18,Fsome sense of closure, knowing justice
OL,19,Fhas been served."
